# FitBite Application

![FitBite Cover Image](cover.png)

## Introduction

FitBite is a user-friendly web application designed to help users track their nutrition and fitness goals. With a sleek interface built using HTML and CSS, FitBite allows users to log their meals, monitor their calorie intake, and stay motivated on their fitness journey.

## Features

- **Meal Logging**: Users can easily log their meals and track their calorie intake.
- **Nutrition Information**: Access to a comprehensive database of nutritional information.
- **Fitness Tracking**: Track workouts and monitor progress toward fitness goals.
- **Responsive Design**: The application is fully responsive and works seamlessly on various devices.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- Visual Studio Code
